	(text "2️⃣ High-Frequency (Decoupling) Capacitors\nWhat they do:\n\nKill switching spikes\n\nProvide instant current at MHz speeds\n\nReduce EMI\n\nKeep IC stable\n\nTypically:\n\n100nF (0.1µF)\n\n10nF sometimes\n\nX7R ceramic\n\nPlaced VERY close to IC pins\n\nThey respond well to:\n\nMHz range\n\nFast edge transitions\n\nSwitching noise"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 18.034 162.306 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "2c2b2639-8f60-4af5-b770-9613bcebd63e")
	)
	(text "1️⃣ Bulk Capacitors (Energy Storage)\nWhat they do:\n\nSupply large current bursts\n\nReduce low-frequency ripple\n\nStabilize load changes (like servo spikes)\n\nTypically:\n\n10µF - 470µF\n\nElectrolytic or large MLCC\n\nHigher ESR than small ceramics\n\nThey respond well to:\n\nkHz range\n\nLoad step changes\n\nMotor / servo bursts"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 15.494 94.234 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "4b09540a-c4be-4fd5-89d4-e4f974ab9a7b")
	)
	(text "Use 10k ohm to make use of full adc range"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 106.934 104.14 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
		)
		(uuid "58768ef0-ebf1-4736-a512-cb96f75b5b72")
	)
	(text "Boost 2 - Servo 3.7V to 5V"
